title: Lebanon Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Lebanon increased to 93684.90 LBP Billion in September from 76680.60 LBP Billion in August of 2022. Money Supply M2 in Lebanon averaged 28445.03 LBP Billion from 1975 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 93684.90 LBP Billion in September of 2022 and a record low of 8.57 LBP Billion in December of 1975. Lebanon Money Supply M2 includes M1 plus short-term time deposits in banks. This page provides - Lebanon Money Supply M2 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Banque Du Liban
